{"tid":2135353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大司法部認定：孟晚舟已符合引渡美國條件","createTime":"2020-08-01T11:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T11:34:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"713d5a1289244b763caecea3f0e0d683c0a804dd","tid":2135353,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"Canada says requirements for Huawei CFO's extradition to U.S. met, documents show<br />\nMoira Warburton<br />\n<br />\n(Reuters) - Canada&rsquo;s attorney general says the requirements for extraditing Huawei Chief Financial Officer Meng Wanzhou to the United States on charges of bank fraud have been met, documents submitted in a British Columbia court show.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-huawei-tech-canada/canada-says-requirements-for-huawei-cfos-extradition-to-u-s-met-documents-show-idUSKCN24W2U1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-huawei-tech-canada%2Fcanada-says-requirements-for-huawei-cfos-extradition-to-u-s-met-documents-show-idUSKCN24W2U1&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Pvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=58d65f37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-huawei-tech-canada%2Fcanada-says-requirements-for-huawei-cfos-extradition-to-u-s-met-documents-show-idUSKCN24W2U1&h=a096176c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-huawei-tech-canada/canada-says-requirements-for-huawei-cfos-extradition-to-u-s-met-documents-show-idUSKCN24W2U1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國科技大廠華為首席財務長孟晚舟引渡案持續進行中，據外媒掌握的官方文件顯示，加拿大司法部門認定孟晚舟已符合引渡美國受審的條件。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，加拿大司法部長兼檢察總長拉梅蒂（David Lametti）在呈交給英屬哥倫比亞法院的文件中明確指出，孟晚舟引渡至美國受審銀行詐欺控訴的條件已符合，「證據顯示孟晚舟蓄意對匯豐銀行做出不實陳述，試圖維護華為與銀行的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3246381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3246381&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Pvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=df417896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3246381&h=05ebe4b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/3246381</a>"},{"pid":"cb7076aafe7988c0a4333f09d9984d822304a248","tid":2135353,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcfc150ff3b59ad50fe1113d0647ce07d60bea08","tid":2135353,"uid":324930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5065e7e0d3c8e8dbe8403e41318b84592a742968","tid":2135353,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d171e60c5beef8fcaa7122a807f2a3d74134e78","tid":2135353,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"hsbc rip"},{"pid":"287addaf7b5a4b53dd2cac2021442cb206412459","tid":2135353,"uid":23221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"快點送佢去美國"},{"pid":"c4f6ea7618f51d067985a36d4d34ddacd835af00","tid":2135353,"uid":160147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"滙豐應記一功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443398b804fee9166e936fdc9bdb6f5e327028f6","tid":2135353,"uid":21592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"可以去美國，不知幾多人想"},{"pid":"afbb5e3f0e5566c3bc0f14dfb182c7e8281f8d8d","tid":2135353,"uid":199540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"雜帝：人黎，賜毒酒！"},{"pid":"62bf35ac9baa8b54229be3b783505c459e745a66","tid":2135